**Data integrity, satisfied by design:**
- Every table has a **PK** (single or composite)
- Every child table has an **FK** back to its parent (`shoe_item→customer`, `repair_job→shoe_item/technician`, `job_service→repair_job/service_type`, `payment→repair_job`)
- **NOT NULL** on every required field, **UNIQUE** on phone/service name, **CHECK** constraints keep status, dates, prices, and payment method valid

